{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore Khorus, a once-thriving world ruled by the Lyramancers, wielders of music-magic, now a decaying land that has lain silent for 1,000 years.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as a bard, given the gift of Lyramancy, who must use their powers to defeat the malevolent god of silence and restore harmony to Khorus.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rhythmic Combat:</strong> Hack and slash wielding a variety of instruments, roll to avoid damage, or play a quick note to parry incoming attacks. Boost damage by chaining <strong>rhythmic combos</strong> with perfectly timed attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/Combat.gif?t=1730663674\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/Parry.gif?t=1730663674\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Lyramancy:</strong> Play songs that conjure powerful magic, release the spirits of fallen foes, or unlock secrets waiting to be discovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/Song.gif?t=1730663674\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Epic Boss Battles:</strong> Bosses provide intense trials and satisfying rewards. Defeating them will get you ever closer to the god of silence that now holds power over Khorus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026740/extras/Boss.gif?t=1730663674\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Exploration:</strong> Run, jump, and climb with precise control to explore a beautiful handcrafted world. Acquire instruments and abilities that open up new pathways and secrets to discover.</p><p class=\"